      <div class="col text">
        <p class="p mt-4 mb-4">As part of my react projects that I completed I had to create a simple change calculator. This calcuclator takes in 
          two inputs from the user; The Total Amount Due and the Total Amount Received. This code is helpful for any business 
          that deals with cash transactions to tell their cashiers exactly how much change to be used. Furthermore, if the business 
          owner wanted to increase effiency even more, they could install automated change dispensers. That change dispenser 
          could use this code to trigger the machine to dispense exactly how many coins to give the customer.
        </p>
